---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Donating — Get Involved"
  description="Donate to Friends of Gledhow Valley Woods — every donation helps fund conservation work, citizen science, and community events in the valley."
  section="get-involved"
>
  <section class="bg-bluebell-800 text-white py-12 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-bluebell-900 to-bluebell-700 opacity-90"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <nav class="text-bluebell-200 font-sans text-sm mb-4" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-white">Home</a> / <a href="/get-involved" class="hover:text-white">Get Involved</a> / <span>Donating</span>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-white">Donating</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="prose prose-lg font-body text-earth-800 max-w-none">
      <p>
        FGVW is a registered charity (no. 1169599), and every donation — large or small — helps fund our conservation work, citizen science water testing programme, and community events like the Green Fair.
      </p>
      <p>
        Donations help us go beyond what membership fees alone can support — from practical conservation projects to acquiring and protecting land in the valley, as we did with <a href="/the-woods/beck-pasture">Beck Pasture</a> in 2016.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- DONATION PROVIDER PLACEHOLDER -->
    <div class="mt-8 border-2 border-dashed border-earth-400 rounded-lg p-6 bg-earth-50">
      <p class="font-sans font-bold text-earth-700 text-sm uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">⚠ DONATION PROVIDER TBC</p>
      <p class="font-body text-earth-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        An online donation option (e.g. via Stripe, PayPal, or a platform such as Localgiving) will be added here once confirmed. In the meantime, please <a href="/contact" class="text-bluebell-700 underline">contact us</a> to arrange a donation by bank transfer or cheque.
      </p>
    </div>
    <!-- END DONATION PLACEHOLDER -->

    <div class="mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-cream-400 flex gap-4 flex-wrap">
      <a href="/get-involved" class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-bluebell-700 hover:underline">← Back to Get Involved</a>
      <a href="/get-involved/volunteering" class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-bluebell-700 hover:underline">Volunteering →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
